### Embeds

Embedding a video:

~~~ .html
<div class="video">
  <!-- Video embed code goes here… -->
</div>
~~~

Embedding an audio:

~~~ .html
<div class="audio">
  <!-- Video embed code goes here… -->
</div>
~~~

Embedding an image with caption:

~~~ .html
<figure class="image">
  <img alt="" src="/path/to/image.jpg">
  <figcaption>Image caption goes here.</figcaption>
</figure>
~~~

Embedding a table with borders:

~~~ .html
<table class="table">
  <caption>Table caption goes here.</caption>
  <!-- Table data goes here… -->
</table>
~~~

